Class LinkedList

  • java.lang.Object
    • LinkedList

  • public class LinkedList
extends java.lang.Object
    The class represents Linked List for Immigration department. The class includes methods for insert, remove, view any candidate in he list, and the complete list of candidates, also methods that allow to search, and remove candidates by name and id
    Author:
    Pedro Alberto Duenas Orozco, Roberto Alejandro Rivera Mejia
